### API root
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/

### List directions
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/directions

### Full timetable
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/timetable

### Lak Hok → Rangsit schedule
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/timetable/lak_hok_to_rangsit

### Lak Hok → Krung Thep Aphiwat schedule
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/timetable/lak_hok_to_krung_thep_aphiwat

### All departures (flat list) – to Bangkok
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/departures?direction=lak_hok_to_krung_thep_aphiwat

### Next train NOW – to Rangsit
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/next?direction=lak_hok_to_rangsit

### Next train at a specific time – to Bangkok
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/next?direction=lak_hok_to_krung_thep_aphiwat&time=08:30
